        <mxCell id="foot" value="Same code, real chip later: a flashed ESP32-CAM replaces section ② and publishes the identical section ③ contract — nothing downstream changes." style="text;html=1;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;fontSize=12;fontColor=#9fb0c3;fontStyle=2;fontFamily=Courier New;" vertex="1" parent="1">
